Well hey there! We=E2=80=99re excited to tell you about our partnership wi=
th Articulation Sitebuilder=2C a new way to create your website quickly an=
d easily =E2=80=94 no coding required. This drag-and-drop builder lets you=
 design a professional-looking site that=E2=80=99s ready to go in minutes=
=2C all within your Porkbun account!

Whether you=E2=80=99re launching a personal project=2C online store=2C or=
 community space=2C Articulation makes it simple to bring your ideas to li=
fe.
LAUNCH YOUR SITE WITH ARTICULATION NOW (https://porkbun.com/products/webho=
sting/articulation?mc_cid=3Dadf0b2f297&mc_eid=3DUNIQID)
Keep reading and learn why Articulation's website editor is just what you=
 need to manage your site at Porkbun!


** WHY IS ARTICULATION SO GREAT?
------------------------------------------------------------
There are a lot of sitebuilders out there=2C but the Articulation sitebuil=
der is designed to give you maximum power without the learning curve. It g=
ives you all the tools you need to grow your web presence without juggling=
 a dozen plugins or writing a single line of code.

=F0=9F=A7=91=E2=80=8D=F0=9F=92=BB Beginner-friendly website builder: Get o=
nline fast with an intuitive drag-and-drop website editor and pre-designed=
 sections that make setup a breeze.

=F0=9F=93=B1 Responsive design by default: Adapts to look great on any scr=
een =E2=80=94 phones=2C tablets=2C and desktops.

=F0=9F=92=B3 Commerce-ready with Stripe integration: Launch your online sh=
op with built-in support for secure payments=2C discounts=2C reviews=2C an=
d inventory tracking.

=F0=9F=93=9D Full-featured blogging platform: Create=2C schedule=2C and ma=
nage blog posts with multiple authors=2C tags=2C and comment tools.

=F0=9F=94=93 Flexible user management and access controls: Add team member=
s or allow site visitors to sign up=2C with fine-tuned permission settings=
 for every role.

=F0=9F=93=8B Built-in form creation tools: Easily collect contact info=2C=
 survey responses=2C and more using the drag-and-drop form builder.


** Website Builder Plans for Every Size
------------------------------------------------------------
We know one size never fits all=2C so the Articulation sitebuilder comes i=
n three tiers:
* Starter: $6/mo or $60/yr. Unlimited pages=2C SSL included=2C plus a stor=
efront for up to 10 products.
* Pro: $12/mo or $120/yr. Adds handy extras like header slideshows=2C site=
 search=2C and storefronts for up to 25 products.
* Performance: $26/mo or $260/yr. Unlimited products=2C memberships=2C and=
 the full range of features.

Every sitebuilder plan includes a free SSL certificate and unlimited pages=
=2C so you can rest easy knowing you=E2=80=99re covered from the start. An=
d as a cherry on top (or maybe an apple in the trough?)=2C when you buy a=
 yearly plan=2C you can snag a domain for free in your first year on selec=
t domain extensions*.

*See the Articulation Site Builder page (https://porkbun.com/products/webh=
osting/articulation?mc_cid=3Dadf0b2f297&mc_eid=3DUNIQID) for the full list=
 of participating domain extensions.


** Who Can Use Articulation Sitebuilder
------------------------------------------------------------
Wondering if Articulation Sitebuilder is right for you? Check out these ki=
nds of websites Articulation makes easy to build and launch:

Personal & Creative Sites
Show off your portfolio=2C photography=2C or personal site with a clean=2C=
 mobile-friendly design.

Online Stores
Sell products=2C digital downloads=2C or subscriptions using built-in e-co=
mmerce tools like inventory tracking=2C coupon codes=2C and SKU management=
=2E

Memberships & Communities
Offer gated content=2C member access=2C and custom forms =E2=80=94 all man=
aged from your dashboard.

Blogs & Publications
Manage posts=2C tags=2C and multiple authors with built-in blogging tools=
 that make publishing easy.

